{"tid":1599433,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【羅冠聰於美國多番強調中国會改變】","createTime":"2019-09-28T03:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:34:27.000Z","uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96141bb8e6962cf84da384f36ff6ffd882914e65","tid":1599433,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"【羅冠聰於美國多番強調中国會改變】<br />\n羅冠聰於昨天參議院東亞委員會聽證會，說了多次他相信(believe)中國會改變*。所以到了2047年他相信香港有機會活在民主中国之下。賣港賊羅冠聰根本是在勸美國不需要做任何事情處理香港2047問題，讓香港順利被中国吞拼就是了。30多年前司徒華用此理由說服香港人要「民主回歸中国」，19年前李柱銘用相同理由說服美國支持中國加入WTO，如今羅冠聰又再用此理由遊說美國要給時間中国改變、 中国改變之後就會讓香港&quot;自決&quot;，所以不需介入2047問題。但「中国會改變」根本就是國際大騙局。所以，請大家向參議院東亞委員會主席Cory Gardner表示並不同意羅冠聰的言論，並說香港人需要美國協助於2047年之前 #實現雙普選、#做好中港區隔、並 #延續美國支持的基本法。<br />\n<br />\n回覆 Cory Gardner的Twitter (請Tag @SenateForeign, @SenCoryGardner, @SenMarkey)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGard&hellip;/status/1177242436499890176&hellip;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGard%E2%80%A6%2Fstatus%2F1177242436499890176%E2%80%A6&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=69577bd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGard&hellip;/status/1177242436499890176&hellip;</a><br />\n<br />\n*來源：We're HongKongers 專頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2407000772890915/posts/2463534977237494/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2407000772890915%2Fposts%2F2463534977237494%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=88006878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2407000772890915/posts/2463534977237494/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2407000772890915/posts/2463610500563275/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2407000772890915%2Fposts%2F2463610500563275%2F&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=3a2ed91d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2407000772890915/posts/2463610500563275/</a><br />\n<br />\n**留言有回覆範例(Amy Ho)"},{"pid":"a8359000952b466bfefe5085a2be2a81bf30b4ed","tid":1599433,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"我唔信黑警會改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1be168c2327b1412ee7bf25c1fcbe7dfc0265f","tid":1599433,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:29:31.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母啦<br />\n佢邊撚個呀？<br />\n憑咩代表港人呀<br />\n食屎啦<br />\n我夠話佢會變到奶共啦"},{"pid":"1d60172c675c98c32444e89f6668921ea4eef176","tid":1599433,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"條友叫佢食屎啦"}]}